@NODE Busy "MUI Royale Guide"
@{b}Overview@{ub}

    Busy class creates an indefinite progress indicator gadget. This is useful
    if you need to indicate a busy state without knowing when processing will be
    finished. For a linear progress indicator, take a look at @{"Gauge class" LINK Gauge}
    instead. See @{"Gauge class" LINK Gauge} for details.

    This class requires at least MUI Royale 1.4.

    @{"Busy.Move                         " LINK BusyMove} Move the busy object
    @{"Busy.Speed                        " LINK BusySpeed} Set/get animation speed
@ENDNODE

@NODE BusyMove "MUI Royale Guide"

   @{b}NAME@{ub}
