        intended to show some kind of percentage information.

        This texts preparse is set to "\\33c\\0338", this makes it appear
        centered and highlighted by default.

        Any %ld will be replaced with the current value of @{"Gauge.Current" LINK GaugeCurrent}.

        Note that if you want to have a single percent character (%) you need to
