        that you can specify here is 16384 pixels.

        To indicate that your Hollywood object has no maximum size, you should
        set this attribute to the maximum allowable size of 16384 pixels. This
        should be sufficiently large enough for most purposes.

        Whenever the user changes the size of your Hollywood object, the
