@NODE ListviewGetEntry "MUI Royale Guide"

   @{b}NAME@{ub}
        Listview.GetEntry -- get listview entry

   @{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
        column1$, ... = mui.DoMethod(id, "GetEntry", pos)

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Get an entry of a list. Pass Active in pos to get the active entry.
        Listview.GetEntry will return the entries of all columns in the row
        specified by pos. You will get as many return values as there are
        columns in the listview.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
        id        id of the listview object
        pos       index of listview row or "Active"

   @{b}RESULTS@{ub}
