   @{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
        mui.DoMethod(id, "Remove", pos)

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Remove an entry from a list. The position can be specified as an
        absolute index value or as one of the following special values:

        First     Remove first entry.

